<H3> <TI>   Talabani, Barzani Meet Iranian Kurdish Party Members </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Talabani, Barzani Meet Iranian Kurdish Party Members </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Iran's Role in Kurdistan Discussed </H4>

<F P=102> NC0506175194 (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan 
in Arabic 1600 GMT 5 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0506175194 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of the People of Kurdistan 
in Arabic 1600 GMT 5 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=105> Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Brother Jalal Talabani, secretary general of the 
Patriotic Union of Kurdistan [PUK] received a delegation of the 
Iranian Kurdistan Democratic Party Political Bureau in his 
office in Irbil at 1700 yesterday. The delegation came to 
welcome his return home. PUK Political Bureau members (Nushiru 
Mustafa), Dr. Fu'ad Ma'sum, and Dr. Kamal Fu'ad also attended 
the meeting. 
  During the meeting, they discussed the situation in Iraqi 
Kurdistan, brother Talabani's peaceful overture, and ways of 
ending the tense situation in Kurdistan. They also discussed 
Iranian interference in Kurdistan's affairs. 
  The delegation expressed appreciation for brother Talabani's 
peaceful initiative and indignation at the interference by 
certain forces which are supported by Iran. 

</TEXT>

