<H3> <TI>   Talabani, Barzani Meet Iranian Kurdish Party Members </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Talabani, Barzani Meet Iranian Kurdish Party Members </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Efforts To Stabilize Situation Viewed </H4>

<F P=102> JN0506081394 (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Kurdistan in 
Arabic 1618 GMT 4 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0506081394 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of Iraqi Kurdistan </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Salah al-Din resort town--Brother Struggler Mas'ud 
Barzani, leader of our Kurdistan Democratic Party [KDP], today, 
4 June 1994, received at the Political Bureau headquarters in 
Salah al-Din resort town, a delegation from the Kurdish 
Democratic Party of Iran [KDPI] led by 'Abdallah Hasan Zadah, 
deputy secretary general and political bureau member of the KDPI. 
  Discussions during the meeting dealt with the current 
situation in Kurdistan and our people's efforts to restore 
normal conditions. 
  The meeting was attended by Sami 'Abd-al-Rahman and 
'Izz-al-Din Barwari, members of the KDP political bureau; and 
(Faransu Hariri), KDP Central Committee member and official in 
charge of national relations. 

</TEXT>

