<F P=105> Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] At his private residence in Irbil last night, 
Brother Jalal Talabani, secretary general of the Patriotic Union 
of Kurdistan, received Major General Hasan al-Naqib, member of 
the Presidium of the Iraqi National Congress [INC], who was 
accompanied by Salah al-Naqib. 
  After Hasan al-Naqib and Salah al-Naqib expressed their 
happiness over the safe return of Brother Talabani from abroad, 
the two sides exchanged views on the present situation in 
Kurdistan, the recent regrettable incidents in the region, and 
the means of normalizing and calming the situation. 

