<F P=102>   JN0506135194 Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network in 
Arabic 1115 GMT 5 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0506135194 </F>
<F P=104>  Damascus Syrian Arab Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] His Excellency President Hafiz al-Asad received Tian 
Zengpei, PRC vice foreign minister, and the delegation 
accompanying him at the al-Rawdah palace at 1300 today. The 
meeting was attended by Foreign Minister Faruq al-Shar' and PRC 
Ambassador in Damascus Li Qingyu. 
  Foreign Minister Faruq al-Shar' received PRC vice foreign 
Minister Tian Zengpei this morning. The meeting was attended by 
Ghassan 'Allush, assistant foreign minister; (Yoran Quangli) 
deputy director of the West Asian and North African Affairs 
department at the PRC Foreign Ministry; and Chinese Ambassador 
in Damascus Li Qingyu. The discussion dealt with the 
international situation, the developments in the region, and the 
latest developments in the peace process. They also discussed 
ways to enhance friendship and cooperation between Syria and the 
PRC. 
  A session of talks has been held between the Syrian side 
under Ghassan 'Allush, assistant foreign minister, and the PRC 
side under Tian Zengpei, PRC vice foreign minister. 

