<H3> <TI>   Council Issues Statement on Resolution </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Council Issues Statement on Resolution </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN0206202494 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
2000 GMT 2 Jun 94 </F>

