  British allies, led by the United States, could only hope 
now 
that London government will come up with something more concrete 
and convincing against Iran next time. 
  Keeping in mind the level of British politicians' 
intelligence, as witnessed recently, the world has to wait for 
quite a long time to hear a single convincing argument against 
Iran from the British side. 

