<F P=100> ARABIAN PENINSULA </F>
<F P=101> Yemen </F>
<H3> <TI>   Qatar Expatriates Raise Funds To Aid War Effort </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Qatar Expatriates Raise Funds To Aid War Effort </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN0206190894 Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network in Arabic 
1700 GMT 2 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0206190894 </F>
<F P=104>  Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
