moved overnight toward the northern border. 
  Our monitor Mikha'el Gurdus reports that Radio Beirut 
reported that the IDF shelled areas north of the security zone 
last night and that Israeli helicopter gunships carried out 
overflights, mainly over Tyre. The sites shelled by the IDF 
artillery are the locations the Katyusha rockets were launched 
from. 

