Sunday. The source said this refinery and other economic 
installations are the property of the Yemeni people and will 
never be a target of the forces of unity and legitimacy. 
Instead, they will be protected and defended by these forces. 
  The source said the hysteria of the elements of the 
rebellious secessionist gang has reached such an extent that 
this criminal gang does not hesitate to commit the most heinous 
crimes against the people, the homeland, and their achievements. 
