<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] This morning, Acting Prime Minister brother Dr. 
Muhammad Sa'id al-'Attar received a delegation from the 
International Committee of the Red Cross [ICRC] led by (Michelle 
Canio), the general ICRC delegate for Middle Eastern and North 
African affairs, and (Arthold Leotold), the regional ICRC 
