<H4>    Technology for Space Research Offered </H4>

<F P=102> BK0706040394 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 0245 
GMT 7 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0706040394 </F>
<F P=104>  Delhi All India Radio Network </F>
