<F P=101> Algeria </F>
<H3> <TI>   Security Services Break Up Large `Terrorist' Unit </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Security Services Break Up Large `Terrorist' Unit </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0606200694 Algiers ENTV Television Network in Arabic 1900 
GMT 6 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0606200694 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers ENTV Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The security services announced today that they had 
broken up a network made up of 60 terrorists after 
two-month-long investigations. Most of the members of the gang 
moved around with forged [identity] cards and specialized in 
theft, armed robbery, sabotage, and murder in Algiers, Blida, 
Boumardes, Bordj Bou Arreridj, and Oran. 

</TEXT>

