<H3> <TI>   UN Envoy Ibrahimi Arrives in Cairo En Route to Yemen </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    UN Envoy Ibrahimi Arrives in Cairo En Route to Yemen </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0706180894 Cairo Arab Republic of Egypt Radio Network in 
Arabic 1730 GMT 7 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> NC0706180894 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo Arab Republic of Egypt Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Lakhdar Ibrahimi, the UN envoy to Yemen, arrived in 
Cairo today from Geneva after meeting with UN Secretary General 
Dr. Butrus Butrus-Ghali, who is currently in Geneva to discuss 
the Yemeni problem. Ibrahimi will also discuss the events in 
Yemen with Egyptian officials. He will travel to Yemen 
afterward, in an attempt to convince the two sides to the 
conflict to adhere to the Security Council resolution issued 
last week that called for an immediate halt to the fighting in 
Yemen. 

</TEXT>

