<F P=100> LEBANON </F>
<H3> <TI>   Roundup of Military Activity in Southern Lebanon </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Roundup of Military Activity in Southern Lebanon </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    `Resistance' Operation in Sujud </H4>

<F P=102> NC0806082894 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0800 GMT 8 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0806082894 </F>
<F P=104>  Beirut Radio Lebanon </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The NATIONAL NEWS AGENCY office in al-Nabatiyah has 
reported that the Israeli occupation forces shelled al-Jabal al- 
Akhdar, al-Jabal al-Rafi', and al-Luwayzah in Iqlim al-Tuffah at 
1030 today while Israeli warplanes flew over the al-Nabatiyah 
and Iqlim al-Tuffah areas. 
  The resistance retaliated against the Israeli aggressions 
today by attacking the Sujud position with rockets and machine 
guns. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

