<F P=100> LEBANON </F>
<H3> <TI>   Roundup of Military Activity in Southern Lebanon </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Roundup of Military Activity in Southern Lebanon </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Katyusha Rockets Land in `Security Zone' </H4>

<F P=102> TA0806111494 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1000 GMT 8 Jun 
94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0806111494 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  Hebrew </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Four katyusha rockets landed today in the security 
zone in the Sujud region. There were no casualties and no 
damage. IDF [Israel Defense Forces] and SLA [South Lebanese 
Army] artillery retaliated by shelling terrorist bases in the 
Iqlim al-Tuffah region. Intermittent exchanges of fire are now 
under way. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

